        substitution placeholders handled by the code (not Android format args).
      · %1$s / %1$d / %1$02d etc. are standard Android format arguments and
        must be preserved verbatim in every translation.
      · &#215; is the multiplication sign ×; keep it as-is.
    =========================================================================
-->
